'''Troféu Imprensa''' (English: ''Press Trophy'', is an award presented annually by [[Sistema Brasileiro de Televisão|SBT]], to honor the best [[Brazilian television]] productions, including [[telenovelas]]. It is known as the "Brazilian [[Academy Awards]]."{{fact|date=January 2018}}

==Awards==
*Best Telenovela
*Best Actor of Telenovela
*Best Actress of Telenovela
*Best Male Singer
*Best Female Singer
*Best Male TV Host
*Best Female TV Host
*Best Talk Show 
*Best Comedy TV Show 
*Best Children's TV Show
*Best Newscast 
*Best Newscast Host
*Best Documentary TV Show
*Best Auditory TV Show
*Best TV Commercial
*Best Musical Group
*Best Song
*Best Country Duo
*Newcomer of the Year (Best New Artist)

